  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can see through falling snow and sleet without taking any penalties on Perception checks as long as there is enough light to allow you to see normally.</p>\n<p>At 11th level, in cold conditions or in icy or snowy terrain, you can learn about your surroundings as if using the @Compendium[pf1.spells.icjrw9y6pa1uatlz]{Commune with Nature} spell.</p>\n<p>You can use the commune with nature ability once per day at 11th level, and twice per day at 15th level.</p>"
